descriptionHtml:
This give Aela a blue colored skin, red Hairs and yellow eyes. The Bikini is from Nikitaa
You have to equip it to her with UFO for example. 

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/11764

Installation:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Just Put the ESP and BSA Files in your Skyrim Data Folder and enable it with the Manager.

Deinstallation:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Erase the Aela files from your Skyrim Data Folder.
